==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Campbellite
<hw>Camp"bell*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<person>Alexander <etsep>Campbell</etsep></person>, of Virginia.]</ety>
<fld>(Eccl.)</fld> <def>A member of the denomination called
<org>Christians or Disciples of Christ</org>. They themselves repudiate
the term <ex>Campbellite</ex> as a nickname. See <er>Christian</er>,
3.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

